  "title": "Logistics Specialist",
  "description": "<p>The selected candidate will be stationed in Singapore and will be responsible for overseeing logistics operations and shipment movements for both Singapore and Malaysia. <br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong><br /><br /><u><strong>Singapore</strong></u></p><ul><li>Coordinate and manage High Jewellery event (Across Southeast Asia) related logistics activities, including periodic reporting</li><li>Consolidate and analyze lead time (LT) and freight performance reports; prepare and upload analytical dashboards to Power BI</li><li>Prepare and maintain duty savings and cost optimization reports</li><li>Resolve daily operational issues, with particular focus on DHL performance monitoring and lead-time control for MA and DHL shipments</li><li>Monitor and follow up on SAP system issues across multiple countries, including Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Philippines, Vietnam, Australia, and New Zealand, ensuring timely escalation and resolution</li><li>Maintain accurate stock card records to support CITES permit applications and regulatory compliance</li></ul><p><u><strong>Malaysia</strong></u></p><ul><li>Review and approve pre-customs declarations for import shipments on a daily basis</li><li>Monitor and manage all import and export shipments, including repair/return, CVM, general supplies, inventory movements, and press samples</li><li>Provide feedback and performance assessments on local customs brokers and logistics service providers to the regional logistics team</li><li>Coordinate and support participation in the Indirect Taxes Voluntary Disclosure Program</li><li>Arrange armed and non-armed courier shipments as required, including high-value deliveries, rebalancing, pull-backs, sold order requests, and HJ transfer</li><li>Manage logistics-related license renewals, including CITES licence renewal</li><li>Manage deposits with local brokers and last-mile service providers, and support the Hong Kong finance team by provided shipment nature and supporting documentation</li><li>Maintain and file tax and logistics records for voluntary disclosure and audit purposes.</li></ul>",
